## About MITT Moscow

MITT (Moscow International Travel & Tourism) is the leading B2B fair for the travel, tourism, and hospitality industry in the CIS region. This major trade show brings together destinations, hotels, tour operators, and travel technology providers from across Russia and neighboring markets.

## Event Focus

Tourism Destinations | Hotels & Accommodation | Tour Operators | Travel Technology | MICE Services | Airlines

## Event Highlights

**500+ Exhibitors** and **20,000+ Visitors** make MITT the premier platform for tourism business in Russia and CIS markets, offering comprehensive B2B networking and deal-making opportunities.

## Why Attend

Access the Russian tourism market, discover CIS destinations, connect with travel professionals, and explore business opportunities in one of the world's largest tourism markets.
